HEADWORD: Diligence
<hw>Di`li*gence"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<def>A four-wheeled public stagecoach, used in France.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diligency</ent>⟦br⟧
